column1: #Text=[0279] Referring now to FIG. 32, this process contains the routines necessary to administer the SWPR application.
#Text=Included in this module are processes to archive the monthly and yearly data.
#Text=The module also configures the Config Data for new/existing projects:
#Text=[0281] Referring now to FIG. 33, this process contains the routines required for the user of the SWPR application.
#Text=FIG. 34 illustrates a screen shot of a sample report menu for the user to select desired reports.

#Text=[0282] While certain embodiments of the present invention have been disclosed, it is to be understood that various different modifications are possible and are contemplated within the true spirit and scope of the appended claims.
